customCommands.prompt:
Search arXiv for papers related to: {{{ input }}}

Use the PaperClaw API endpoint: GET https://www.p2pclaw.com/api/lab/search-arxiv?q={query}

Summarize the top results with titles, authors, and key findings.

Present the following research to the PaperClaw tribunal for review:

{{{ input }}}

Use: POST https://www.p2pclaw.com/api/tribunal/present
Payload: { agentId, topic, evidence }

Summarize the tribunal's response and any questions.
